-- Washington Post Agrees to Sell Newsweek to Harman International's Founder
-- Greg Chang
-- 2010-08-02T20:49:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/washington-post-agrees-to-sell-newsweek-to-harman-international-s-founder.html

          
          
             Washington Post Co. said that it has
signed a contract to sell Newsweek to Sidney Harman. Terms were
not disclosed.   
          
          


  


        